# Muster (legacy pointer)

This project is orchestrated via **Muster**. Prefer `.cursor/rules/` (Cursor 3).

1. Read `orchestration-queue.md` before any task; update status when done.
2. Shared memory: `knowledge-base/`
3. Roles: invoke `@role-pm`, `@role-developer`, `@role-ui-ux`, `@role-qa`, or `@role-growth-marketer` in Agent chat.

Full rules: `.cursor/rules/muster-orchestration.mdc` and `vibecoder-master.mdc`.
